<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.9">
<l>pērāṉaik kuṭantaip perumāṉai yilaṅkoḷicēr</l>
<l>vārār vaṉamulaiyāḷ malarmaṅkai nāyakaṉai</l>
<l>ārāviṉ ṉamutaitteṉ ṉaḻuntaiyil maṉṉiniṉṟa</l>
<l>kārār karumukilaik kaṇṭukoṇṭuka ḷittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself the one of Pēr, the lord of Kuṭantai,</l>
<l>Husband of the lady on the blossom - the one with lovely breasts</l>
<l>With a bodice with shining splendor, the never-sating sweet nectar,</l>
<l>The dark rain-filled cloud who stands eternally in Aḻuntai in the south,</l>
<l rend="indent">I was reeling!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
